{"about_the_game":"<strong>Throw magic bombs! Destroy everything around you! Avenge your family!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u25c6 Hand-drawn levels that you can destroy! \u25c6</strong></h2>Make tunnels, destroy walls, use the terrain to your advantage! Every level contains terrain that can be destroyed with bombs.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/terrain.gif?t=1685448039\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u25c6 Elemental bombs with unique effects! \u25c6</strong></h2>There are 8 unique bomb types for the player to unlock, each with unique effects!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong><i>Normal Bomb:</i></strong> A simple explosion. Very reliable!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/bomb_normal_200.png?t=1685448039\" /><br></li><li> <strong><i>Electric Bomb:</i></strong> Spawns an Electric Star that zaps nearby enemies. (WARNING: Very volatile!)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/bomb_electric_200.png?t=1685448039\" /><br></li><li> <strong><i>And more!</i></strong> (Play the game to find them all!)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/bomb_wind_200_HIDDEN.png?t=1685448039\" /></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u25c6 Interactions and reactions between bombs (and the environment)! \u25c6</strong></h2><br>Most bombs can react with each other or the environment to create something new!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <i>Throw an electric bomb at lava and watch it <strong>explode!</strong></i><br></li><li> <i>Make enemies shoot fireballs into an ice cloud to deal <strong>bonus damage</strong> to them!</i><br></li><li> <i>And <strong>more!</strong></i></li></ul><br>Use these combinations to your advantage!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"http